snippet.title: Roadmap Summer 2021 - A Glimpse Of Luna (Card Game)
snippet.description:
In this video we show you the roadmap summer 2021 for the tactical battle card game. We have some exciting events coming up. Register on our website - https://www.glimpse-luna.com/register - so you don´t miss out on any of those events. 

Visit our website: https://www.glimpse-luna.com/
Join our Discord-Server: https://discord.gg/Tmk8yY2UsY
Join our Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/GlimpseOfLuna/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayGlimpseLuna

Music by Adrian von Ziegler:
https://adrianvonziegler.bandcamp.com/
